				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">"WP:3" redirects here. You may be looking for <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Trifecta" title="Wikipedia:Trifecta">Wikipedia:Trifecta</a>, <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Triple_Crown" title="Wikipedia:Triple Crown">Wikipedia:Triple Crown</a>, or <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Three-revert_rule" class="mw-redirect" title="Wikipedia:Three-revert rule">Wikipedia:Three-revert rule</a>.</div>
